title: AWS EC2: Instance Disk IO
agents: aws
catalog: cloud/aws
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors

 - completed read and write operations

 - read and write throughput

 to all instance store volumes available to the instance.

 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Amazon Web Services (AWS)}.

item:
 Name of the instance

inventory:
 One service is created for each disk if all required metrics
 (ReadOps, WriteOps, ReadBytes and WriteBytes) are given.
